This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: my celestial white noise
des:
Listen to Celestial White Noise, make it nice and quiet.

My Celestial White Noice provides a high quality white noise sound for 10 hours.

To start, just say "Alexa, play My Celestial White Noise".

At anytime, you can stop the audio by saying "Alexa, stop"
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
